Dichloromethane selectively dissolve caffeine without carrying sugars, peptides, flavor ingredients, remove coffee's buzz without changing taste. However, somewhat toxic, evidence suggested might carcinogenic, use sharply curtailed.

Ethyl acetate used replacement dichloromethane 80's early 90's. Although moderately toxic, coffee maker touted ethyl acetate "natural" present fruit.

A nontoxic environmentally benign solvent either dichloromethane ethyl acetate used: supercritical fluid carbon dioxide. 

When sealed vial containing gaseous liquid carbon dioxide high pressure heated, liquid density drop gas density rises. If pressure 72.8 atm, temperature rise 304.2 K, density liquid density gas become identical. The meniscus liquid gas phase vanishes. The carbon dioxide becomes supercritical fluid gaslike liquidlike properties. The fluid fill container like gas, dissolve substance like liquid. Supercritical fluid carbon dioxide excellent nonpolar solvent many organic compounds, including caffeine.

The extraction process simple. Supercritical carbon dioxide forced green coffee beans. Its gaslike behavior allows penetrate deep beans, dissolve 97 99% caffeine present. The caffeine valuable, coffee manufacturer usually try recover it. The caffeine laden CO2 sprayed high pressure water caffeine isolated variety methods, including charcoal adsorption, distillation, recrystallization, reverse osmosis.
